WEBVTT

00:00:56.927 --> 00:01:00.434
HAYOM TISHA ASAR BEFEBRUAR ELEF UNK TISHIM VESHEVA

00:01:00.434 --> 00:01:03.227
ANI ZIPI KICHLER MERAYENET ET

00:01:03.238 --> 00:01:06.354
HUGO HERSHI TSVI FISHMAN

00:01:06.478 --> 00:01:08.548
BECHOLON, BEYIDISH

00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:11.445
UNK

00:01:11.456 --> 00:01:12.581
SHALOM

00:01:12.975 --> 00:01:14.286
vi heyst ir?

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:17.662
ikh heys Fishman Hugo.

00:01:18.025 --> 00:01:21.948
ober alts kindvayz hot men mikh gerufn Hershi.

00:01:22.259 --> 00:01:24.454
un azoy hob ikh geheysn

00:01:24.454 --> 00:01:29.961
biz toyznt nayn hundert fertsik, ven di ungarn zenen arayngekumen,

00:01:30.025 --> 00:01:34.259
denstmol bin ikh gevoyr gevorn az ikh heys Hugo,

00:01:34.519 --> 00:01:39.454
un oyf yidish Hershi. dos heyst oyf ivrit Tsvi.

00:01:40.481 --> 00:01:42.493
vu zent inen geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:41.868 --> 00:01:44.971
geboyrn gevorn bin ikh in aza shtot

00:01:44.971 --> 00:01:48.664
velkhe ir ir gesheenishn

00:01:49.077 --> 00:01:50.649
shpiglt op

00:01:50.649 --> 00:01:52.532
dem gantsn yo-,

00:01:52.532 --> 00:01:56.129
di gantse virtshaft fun dem yorhundert.

00:01:56.415 --> 00:01:59.194
dey shtot hot geheysn Uzhgorod.

00:01:59.974 --> 00:02:01.207
deys...

00:01:59.988 --> 00:02:02.024
vu iz dos geven, in Rumenye?

00:02:01.779 --> 00:02:04.506
nayn, deys vil ikh itster zogn.

00:02:04.636 --> 00:02:09.857
biz toyznt nayn hundert akhtsn, hot deys gehert tsu Estraykh-Ungarn.

00:02:10.259 --> 00:02:12.519
in toyznt nayn hundert akhtsik

00:02:12.519 --> 00:02:15.831
akhtsn iz deys gevorn Tshekhoslovakay.

00:02:15.974 --> 00:02:19.363
s'iz endikt gevorn di tsvey- di ershte velt milkhome,

00:02:19.363 --> 00:02:21.922
iz deys gevorn Tshekhoslovakay.

00:02:22.129 --> 00:02:27.805
deys iz geven biz toyznt nayn hundert naynem un draysik iz deys geven Tshekhoslovakay.

00:02:27.870 --> 00:02:31.415
denstmol zenen arayngekumen di Ungern, vayl di

00:02:31.415 --> 00:02:33.389
fashistishe Daytshland

00:02:33.389 --> 00:02:36.272
hot tseshmetert Tshekhoslovakay,

00:02:36.415 --> 00:02:38.701
iz deys gevorn Ungarn.

00:02:38.701 --> 00:02:42.337
hot deys shoyn geheysn Ungvar, nisht Uzhgorod.

00:02:42.688 --> 00:02:48.688
azoy iz deys geven biz toyznt nayn hundert fir un fertsik, ven se zenen arayngekumen di rusn.

00:02:48.896 --> 00:02:51.818
un di rusn hobn deys gemakht

00:02:51.857 --> 00:02:53.896
vider Uzhgorod.

00:02:55.246 --> 00:03:00.987
di rusn hobn deys gehaltn

00:03:01.350 --> 00:03:04.753
biz toyznt nayn hundert

00:03:05.948 --> 00:03:10.064
 nayntsik, eynem un nayntsik ven

00:03:10.090 --> 00:03:12.961
Sovyet Rusnland hot zikh oyfgeleyzt,

00:03:13.025 --> 00:03:15.311
iz deys gevorn Ukrayne.

00:03:15.571 --> 00:03:18.350
azoy az finef medines

00:03:18.376 --> 00:03:21.376
hobn gehersht iber der shtot.

00:03:22.467 --> 00:03:29.124
dort bin ikh geboyrn gevorn. in toyznt nayn hundert nayntsn in khoydesh november.

00:03:24.067 --> 00:03:25.400
velkhes yor?

00:03:29.124 --> 00:03:34.020
ober durkhgevekt, azoy gezogt, mayne oygn, ikh zol zen di velt,

00:03:34.020 --> 00:03:36.854
hob ikh mikh durkhgevekt in Rozavlye.

00:03:36.857 --> 00:03:38.688
deys iz a dorf

00:03:38.833 --> 00:03:41.584
vos se gefint zikh oyf an anderer gegnt,

00:03:41.584 --> 00:03:46.354
in Rumenye, in der gegnt vos se heyst Maramuresh.

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:53.812
deys iz a sh-, dort iz do a shtot Siget, fun dem zibenem un draysik kilometer.

00:03:53.854 --> 00:03:56.207
deys iz geven deys dorf

00:03:56.207 --> 00:03:58.937
fun vu mayn tate hot geshtamt.

00:03:58.937 --> 00:04:03.791
dort hobn gevoynt zayne eltern, dos heyst mayn babe un mayn zeyde,

00:04:03.818 --> 00:04:07.791
azoy az in toyznt nayn hundert tsvontsik

00:04:07.805 --> 00:04:11.270
hot zikh mayn tate mit der gantse familye

00:04:11.272 --> 00:04:14.844
tsurik ibergetsoygn keyn Rozavlye, fun

00:04:14.844 --> 00:04:18.041
Uzhgorod, fun yener gegnt, deys iz geven in

00:04:18.041 --> 00:04:19.649
Karpatn gebit,

00:04:19.662 --> 00:04:22.666
in Maramuresh, keyn Siget.

00:04:23.055 --> 00:04:25.783
vi hobn zey geheysn, di eltern un di...?

00:04:25.581 --> 00:04:26.883
di...

00:04:25.957 --> 00:04:27.124
di bobe mit...

00:04:26.883 --> 00:04:31.792
der zeyde hot geheysn Fishman Yankl.

00:04:32.155 --> 00:04:35.013
un di babe hot geheysn Rivke.

00:04:35.090 --> 00:04:39.532
deys vil ikh zogn, az ven ikh hob geefnt di oygn, dos heyst ven ikh hob,

00:04:39.571 --> 00:04:42.467
ikh gedenk azoy far mir di velt,

00:04:42.467 --> 00:04:45.311
iz geven der ershter der zeyde.

00:04:45.363 --> 00:04:47.896
mayn zeyde iz geven a rebe

00:04:47.896 --> 00:04:49.285
vos hot gehat a kheyder.

00:04:49.285 --> 00:04:51.714
nisht a rebe a rov a

00:04:51.844 --> 00:04:55.285
a a rebe vos hot gelernt kinder.

00:04:55.506 --> 00:04:59.207
hot mikh mayn mame hot gefirt tsun im

00:04:59.675 --> 00:05:02.701
lernen. deys iz nokh geven, ikh bin nokh geven,

00:05:02.701 --> 00:05:05.000
ikh veys tsi ikh bin alt geven fir yor.

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.272
un azoy vi a nepl,

00:05:07.272 --> 00:05:11.207
kumt mir deys for, bin ikh, hot men mikh gefirt tsun im

00:05:11.716 --> 00:05:12.310
lernen.

00:05:12.870 --> 00:05:15.416
er iz geven mit a langer bord,

00:05:15.604 --> 00:05:20.187
ikh gedenk azoy vi haynt, a sakh zakhn gedenk ikh nisht fun im, vayl ikh bin geven kleyn,

00:05:20.187 --> 00:05:21.999
er hot gehat aza

00:05:22.104 --> 00:05:24.020
shtekn lebn zikh,

00:05:24.020 --> 00:05:26.166
un mit dem fleg er zikh alts dem

00:05:26.187 --> 00:05:28.291
rukn araynshtupn baym hemd,

00:05:28.291 --> 00:05:30.979
un dort zikh sh- vayl se hot im geshmartst.

00:05:31.020 --> 00:05:33.657
nu, iz er geven shoyn an elterer mentsh,

00:05:33.814 --> 00:05:39.585
vifl ikh hob gelernt bayn im gedenk ikh nisht azoy veys ikh, nor deys gedenk ikh az er iz geshtorbn.

00:05:39.828 --> 00:05:41.428
deys ken zayn

00:05:41.428 --> 00:05:43.014
a yor tsi aroyf,

00:05:43.328 --> 00:05:47.018
tsvey yor nisht, vayl fun zeks yor heyb ikh shoyn on tsu gedenken.

00:05:47.214 --> 00:05:52.287
azoy bayleyfik a yor hob ikh bay dem rebe, bay mayn zeyde gelernt

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:56.885
alef beys, vifl me hot gelernt bay deye fir yor.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:06:04.128
nu shoyn, er iz geshtorbn, nokh dem bin ikh aribergegangen nokh an andern kheyder.

00:06:04.257 --> 00:06:09.671
shoyn geherik a melamed vu me lernt kinder, un dort hob ikh gelernt.

00:06:09.772 --> 00:06:11.910
vi hobn geheysn dayne eltern?

00:06:11.885 --> 00:06:13.314
itst mayn

00:06:13.314 --> 00:06:16.457
z-da- tate hot geheysn Dovid.

00:06:16.728 --> 00:06:19.542
un di mame hot geheysn Feyge.

00:06:19.948 --> 00:06:21.141
fun der heym?

00:06:20.785 --> 00:06:23.385
fun der heym, Feyge Goldshteyn.

00:06:23.528 --> 00:06:26.728
un der tate hot geheysn Fishman Dovid.

00:06:27.371 --> 00:06:34.728
der emes gezogt az ikh, ven ikh bin shoyn ongehoybn tsu derkenen di velt, azoy gezen tsvishn mir,

00:06:34.728 --> 00:06:38.142
iz der tate shoyn nisht geven bayn undz in der heym.

00:06:38.771 --> 00:06:41.028
er iz zikh avekgeforn

00:06:41.100 --> 00:06:44.200
in an anderer gegnt in Rumenye,

00:06:44.271 --> 00:06:50.614
azoy hot dos geheysn Bakoy, deys iz oyf a, in Moldova azoy zogt men deys dort bayn undz,

00:06:50.614 --> 00:06:54.071
un di mame iz geblibn dort aleyn,

00:06:54.071 --> 00:06:56.614
mit di kinder. ze'mir geven...

00:06:55.335 --> 00:06:56.578
vifl zenen...

00:06:57.071 --> 00:07:00.100
ikh, ze'mir geven fir meydlekh,

00:07:00.100 --> 00:07:02.242
un ikh eyn yingl.

00:07:02.585 --> 00:07:05.328
eyn, ikh bin geven der ferter,

00:07:05.342 --> 00:07:07.885
un nokh mir iz nokh geven eyn meydl.

00:07:07.755 --> 00:07:10.382
zog di nemen fun di ale kinder.

00:07:09.375 --> 00:07:19.100
der, di ershte, mayn shvester, di eltste, iz geven Sime. azoy hot zi geheysn. oyf ungerish hot men deys gerufn SZERENA. ober Sime iz zi geven.

00:07:19.157 --> 00:07:22.500
di ande- tsveyte iz geven Leye,

00:07:22.814 --> 00:07:25.828
di drite iz geven Beyle,

00:07:25.942 --> 00:07:28.900
ikh, der ferter, Hershi,

00:07:28.928 --> 00:07:32.942
un di finfte, dos yungste meydl iz geven Sori.

00:07:33.871 --> 00:07:36.000
nu, ikh gedenk

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.857
der tate iz shoyn nisht geven bay der familye,

00:07:38.923 --> 00:07:42.141
fun vu, vos iz geven der parnose?

00:07:40.200 --> 00:07:42.249
fun vos me hot gelebt,

00:07:43.242 --> 00:07:50.100
az in emesdik zogn, fun ven ikh gedenk nokh, nor fun denstmol ken ikh zogn, az befor

00:07:50.100 --> 00:07:51.585
iz geven

00:07:52.514 --> 00:07:56.714
az der zeyde, heyst di babe shoyn,

00:07:56.728 --> 00:07:59.200
hobn epes geshtitst,

00:07:59.257 --> 00:08:04.214
un der tate fleg shikn a por LEI, vifl

00:08:04.214 --> 00:08:07.171
veys ikh nisht, a por LEI fleg er shikn

00:08:07.342 --> 00:08:13.028
oyf aheym, un di mame, a sakh mol fleg geyn, nisht oyf shtendik,

00:08:13.028 --> 00:08:14.442
oyf farshidene

00:08:14.442 --> 00:08:16.457
balebatim in dorf,

00:08:16.457 --> 00:08:18.600
shtopn gendz,

00:08:18.793 --> 00:08:22.014
kokhn,

00:08:22.214 --> 00:08:26.657
un fun dem hot men gelebt, ober gants shver.

00:08:26.942 --> 00:08:33.328
ven ikh hob shoyn ongehoybn tsu derkenen azoy dos lebn, iz shoyn mayn, di eltste shvester

00:08:33.328 --> 00:08:37.642
shoyn geven avekgegangen fun der heym keyn Siget,

00:08:37.642 --> 00:08:38.971
in der shtot,

00:08:39.171 --> 00:08:42.714
un dort hot zi ongehoybn tsu arbetn,

00:08:42.885 --> 00:08:45.800
do zogt men deys haynt OZERET.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.942
dort hot men deys gezogt a dinst,

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:54.357
oyf a plats, un gearbet bay gendz. yener balebos

00:08:54.357 --> 00:08:56.800
hot gehat a gesheft, der hot

00:08:56.942 --> 00:09:00.900
oyfgearbet gendz, farkoyft fleysh mit vos ven,

00:09:00.900 --> 00:09:04.471
un dort hot zi gearbet, deys iz geven a shvere arbet.

00:09:05.185 --> 00:09:11.628
deroyf oyf a yor tsvey, hot zi aroysgenumen di andere shvester, Leye, keyn, oykh keyn Siget.

00:09:11.871 --> 00:09:17.042
un deye iz gevorn a shtrikerin, dey iz arayngegangen in a shtrikeray.

00:09:17.042 --> 00:09:19.971
azoy hot geheysn di ershte shtrikeray,

00:09:19.971 --> 00:09:21.400
Terkltoyb.

00:09:21.857 --> 00:09:24.228
azoy hobn zey geheysn, di balebatim.

00:09:24.542 --> 00:09:26.671
un dey tsvey meydlekh,

00:09:26.671 --> 00:09:30.714
zenen denstmol alt geven, se hot gekent zayn, zogn mir in

00:09:31.014 --> 00:09:35.514
finef un tsvontsik zeks un tsvontsik, bayleyfik,

00:09:35.557 --> 00:09:40.385
un di eltste shvester iz geven a geboyrene in nayn, in nayn.

00:09:40.442 --> 00:09:42.871
hot zi gebroykht zayn

00:09:42.900 --> 00:09:45.128
a zekhtsn zibetsn yor

00:09:45.128 --> 00:09:47.057
ven zi iz arayngegangen.

00:09:47.057 --> 00:09:51.828
un di tsveyte, velkhe iz geven yinger mit tsvey yor, oykhet bayleyfik bay di

00:09:51.828 --> 00:09:53.742
zekhtsn yor arayngegangen.

00:09:54.014 --> 00:09:56.828
nu, deye hobn shoyn geshikt a por

00:09:57.110 --> 00:09:59.542
LEI aheym far der mame,

00:10:00.161 --> 00:10:02.401
in der tsayt, di drite shvester

00:10:02.973 --> 00:10:06.677
hot men, iz zi avekgeforn tsu mayn mames eltern,

00:10:06.790 --> 00:10:08.550
mayn mames mishpokhe,

00:10:09.041 --> 00:10:11.629
velkhe zey hobn gelebt in Tshekhoslovakay,

00:10:11.894 --> 00:10:14.984
se heyst undz ho'mir gelebt in Rumenye, in Siget,

00:10:15.073 --> 00:10:17.652
un zey hobn gelebt in der Ukraynes

00:10:17.815 --> 00:10:20.063
Subkarpatika, azoy hot dos geheysn.

00:10:20.352 --> 00:10:22.489
dortn ahin hot men zi geshikt.

00:10:22.889 --> 00:10:23.673
dort

00:10:23.689 --> 00:10:27.605
hot zi gevoynt, gegesn, un zi iz gevorn a bisl greser

00:10:27.742 --> 00:10:31.884
iz zi oykh gegangen dort arbetn, oykhet oyf a dinst.

00:10:32.152 --> 00:10:34.863
oyf pletser vu zi hot dort gearbet.

00:10:35.479 --> 00:10:37.947
un eyn mol in a yor

00:10:37.979 --> 00:10:40.177
fleg men aheymkumen, oyf

00:10:40.177 --> 00:10:41.687
rosheshone,

00:10:41.802 --> 00:10:44.739
fleg zikh di familye azoy in gantsn

00:10:44.822 --> 00:10:45.937
tsamkumen.

00:10:46.729 --> 00:10:54.833
der tate, in di gantse tsayt vos ikh gedenk az er iz geven tsvey mol in der heym, dos heyst fun toyznt

00:10:55.177 --> 00:10:59.406
nayn hundert, zogn mir, finef un tsvontsik, zeks un tsvontsik,

00:10:59.406 --> 00:11:02.083
biz toyznt nayn hundert

00:11:02.614 --> 00:11:07.343
naynem un tsvontsik vos undz ho'mir dort gevoynt in Rozavlye,

00:11:07.354 --> 00:11:09.833
iz er dort geven eyn mol.

00:11:09.906 --> 00:11:12.572
di gantse por yorn. azoy az er iz nisht

00:11:12.604 --> 00:11:13.416
gelebt.

00:11:13.416 --> 00:11:17.064
mayn mame hot zikh azoy geplogt mit di kinder, un zi hot zey gehaltn.

00:11:17.406 --> 00:11:20.288
ikh bin vayter gegangen in kheyder,

00:11:20.864 --> 00:11:28.958
un, in kheyder azoy vi ale yidishe kinder hobn dort gelernt, hob ikh oykhet, ikh bin nisht geven keyn shlekhter

00:11:28.958 --> 00:11:31.062
lerer, ikh hob gut gelernt,

00:11:31.979 --> 00:11:34.072
un,

00:11:34.343 --> 00:11:36.489
ikh hob gehat gute

00:11:36.489 --> 00:11:40.406
vi azoy men zogt, melamedn, velkhe zey hobn geven, zey zenen geven,

00:11:40.406 --> 00:11:43.895
eyner iz, eyner iz geven, vi azoy me zogt do,

00:11:43.895 --> 00:11:48.010
ULTRA frum.

00:11:48.041 --> 00:11:54.229
der anderer iz geven tsveyte UNK ULTRA frum, un er fleg araynkumen, iz gezesn dort kinder un lernen,

00:11:54.322 --> 00:11:58.166
un eyner iz geshtanen, zog mir azoy, hot er deys nisht gelozt,

00:11:58.239 --> 00:12:03.552
"vayl deys heyst a a tseylem," zogt er, "deys tor men nisht." dos gedenk ikh nokhn bizn hayntikn tog,

00:12:03.552 --> 00:12:06.708
zogt er, "deys tor men nisht azoy haltn di k- di hent."

00:12:07.041 --> 00:12:12.958
in dorf iz geven a kloyster, un farn kloyster iz geven aza tseylem, mit mit

00:12:12.958 --> 00:12:16.645
Yosele Pandrik, hot men gezogt denstmol, bay di yidn, azoy hot men

00:12:16.645 --> 00:12:17.895
gebroykht rufn

00:12:17.927 --> 00:12:20.270
JESUS JESUSn.

00:12:20.437 --> 00:12:21.677
Yosele Pandrik,

00:12:21.874 --> 00:12:25.062
zogt er, "ven me geyt durkh lebn yenem," zogt er

00:12:25.062 --> 00:12:27.843
"broykh men zogn yimakh-shemoy..."

00:12:27.843 --> 00:12:30.947
mit, ikh gedenk nisht nokh epes a vort.

00:12:30.968 --> 00:12:35.531
shoyn, azoy in deye rabonim zenen dort geven,

00:12:35.770 --> 00:12:40.572
ober dos dorf, di yidn dort hobn gevoynt bayleyfik bayn a

00:12:40.895 --> 00:12:44.416
tsvey hundert un fuftsik, dray hundert mishpokhes.

00:12:44.416 --> 00:12:47.541
se iz geven gants a a groyse dorf mit yidn.

00:12:47.541 --> 00:12:52.604
yidn hobn dort gelebt a yidish lebn, geven a dayen, geven a

00:12:52.604 --> 00:12:54.416
shoykhet,

00:12:54.416 --> 00:12:59.979
mentshn zenen gegangen in shul yedn tog, yedn tsu fri, oyf der nakht, un shabes un,

00:12:59.999 --> 00:13:03.395
ikh shmues nisht fun rosheshone un andere yontoyvim,

00:13:03.427 --> 00:13:04.468
deys iz geven.

00:13:04.552 --> 00:13:09.384
un andere iz geven yontoyvim. mentshn hobn gelebt take shver,

00:13:09.968 --> 00:13:14.354
un vi azoy me hot gekent, veys, der tsveyter rebe mayne iz geven

00:13:14.354 --> 00:13:16.999
Anshl der beder, azoy hot men im geheysn.

00:13:17.437 --> 00:13:21.499
nu, Anshl der beder hot gehat a tokhter

00:13:21.552 --> 00:13:25.499
a sheyne, vos hobn geheysn Anshl der beder, vayl bayn im iz geven di mikve.

00:13:25.624 --> 00:13:30.677
dort flegn geyn di mener, un eyn mol in der vokh, di vayber di froyen,

00:13:30.749 --> 00:13:32.208
un dort iz geven di mikve.

00:13:32.697 --> 00:13:35.604
der Anshl der beder hot gehat a tokhter,

00:13:35.604 --> 00:13:40.312
nu, oykhet, er iz oykh geven fun yene balebatim, er iz geven an oremer mentsh,

00:13:40.437 --> 00:13:44.229
un az di tokhter iz geven a geherike, a sheyne meydl vos ven,

00:13:44.468 --> 00:13:47.979
eyn mol kumt er arayn un zogt undz, "nu,

00:13:47.979 --> 00:13:49.927
hot ir gezen mayn eydem?"

00:13:50.770 --> 00:13:51.781
zogt er,

00:13:51.791 --> 00:13:57.135
"er iz a voyler bokher, se felt im nor sheyn gut ven," zogt er, "er makht er a bisl azoy mit di oygn."

00:13:57.312 --> 00:14:01.697
"nu s'iz nisht keyn groyse maler," zog mir undz, az s'iz azoyns.

00:14:02.052 --> 00:14:05.802
plutsem azoy nokh mitog, kumt arayn

00:14:06.562 --> 00:14:09.001
a kleyntshiker, mit a pukl,

00:14:09.001 --> 00:14:11.229
vos heyst a pukl?

00:14:11.343 --> 00:14:13.978
un ikh ze der makht takn azoy,

00:14:14.870 --> 00:14:17.812
nu, un do azoy ayngefaln, vos ven,

00:14:17.864 --> 00:14:20.333
nu az der iz takn a,

00:14:20.520 --> 00:14:24.593
a guter khosn, iz er takn a gutn khosn. shoyn azoy...

00:14:24.687 --> 00:14:29.572
un vi azoy ikh bin takn gevoyr gevorn, er hot gehat a lungen krankeyt,

00:14:29.593 --> 00:14:32.135
un deroyf oyf a por yor iz er takn

00:14:32.260 --> 00:14:36.427
opgeshtorbn. nor ikh meyn az vi azoy me hot gelebt dort,

00:14:36.427 --> 00:14:37.416
di mentshn.

00:14:38.385 --> 00:14:42.844
bay di zibn yor, hob ikh shoyn ongehoybn tsu geyn in shul.

00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:46.656
in kheyder bayn undz hot men gelernt nisht nor

00:14:46.864 --> 00:14:51.218
toyre, davenen, vos ven, me hot gelernt shraybn rumenish,

00:14:51.218 --> 00:14:52.916
un rekhenen in rumenish.

00:14:53.187 --> 00:14:59.010
azoy ven ikh bin gegangen in shul bay di zibn yor, dos heyst ikh bin gegangen dray fir yor in kheyder biz denstmol,

00:14:59.010 --> 00:15:01.374
hob ikh shoyn gekent gut rekhenen.

00:15:02.197 --> 00:15:04.364
un ikh bin ahingekumen in shul,

00:15:04.489 --> 00:15:10.760
iz shoyn mayn lererke geven, in rumenishe shul, dortn fun sta- fun der medine UNK,

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:13.830
dort zenen gegangen in eynem rumenishe kinder mit

00:15:13.854 --> 00:15:15.121
yidishe kinder.

00:15:15.121 --> 00:15:17.674
in dem dorf hobn gevoynt nor rumener.

00:15:17.812 --> 00:15:20.800
un gegangen in der

00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:24.371
shul, zeyer gut, geven,

00:15:24.426 --> 00:15:26.045
se iz nisht geven keyn shum

00:15:26.119 --> 00:15:29.329
makhloykes tsvishn, nisht tsvishn di kinder,

00:15:29.329 --> 00:15:31.798
un ikh gedenk nisht in di gantse yorn

00:15:31.845 --> 00:15:36.840
az tsvishn di mentshn, tsvishn di rumener un tsvishn yidn, zol geven dort epes a min

00:15:36.904 --> 00:15:39.494
problem. me hot gelebt gut, besholem,

00:15:39.531 --> 00:15:40.836
ales het iz geven.

00:15:41.206 --> 00:15:46.330
nu, azoy vi ikh dort gelernt, dos lernen iz gegangen gants gut,

00:15:46.479 --> 00:15:49.178
un me hob gemuzt a bisl epes

00:15:49.178 --> 00:15:51.150
helfn in der shtub oykhet.

00:15:51.246 --> 00:15:52.835
fleg ikh alts geyn,

00:15:53.863 --> 00:15:55.671
dort iz do a sakh

00:15:55.671 --> 00:15:57.958
gertner mit oyps,

00:15:58.223 --> 00:16:01.986
s-, nisht YERAKOT

00:15:59.925 --> 00:16:00.706
PEROT.

00:16:00.706 --> 00:16:01.893
PEROT.

00:16:01.986 --> 00:16:02.736
vi azoy?

00:16:02.850 --> 00:16:03.420
PEROS.

00:16:03.406 --> 00:16:04.460
PEROT, yo.

00:16:04.876 --> 00:16:07.796
 geven, bin ikh gegangen kloybn epl.

00:16:07.821 --> 00:16:09.726
yedn, kh-

00:16:09.726 --> 00:16:15.520
in di khadoshim fun september un oktober fleg ikh geyn kloybn epl.

00:16:15.630 --> 00:16:17.287
un dort fardint a por

00:16:17.301 --> 00:16:20.123
LEI un aheymgebrengt alts a bisl

00:16:20.123 --> 00:16:21.643
epl, vi azoy me zogt.

00:16:22.137 --> 00:16:25.369
shpeter bin ikh nokh gegangen kloybn UNK.

00:16:25.452 --> 00:16:31.137
deys iz oykh geven in dey shpeterdike yorn, vayl dort iz geven balebatim, yidishe balebatim,

00:16:31.219 --> 00:16:33.739
se geven a familye Shtern,

00:16:33.808 --> 00:16:37.506
 geven gute UNK, zey hobn gehat dort a

00:16:37.506 --> 00:16:39.808
a hundert hundert fuftsik hektar

00:16:39.808 --> 00:16:42.780
feld, deys iz geven dort a zeyer a sakh,

00:16:43.000 --> 00:16:50.328
nu, un dort iz men gegangen alts yedn ahin, fleg'mir geyn, ikh un di mame, un mit der klenerer shvester, vi azoy me zogt, mit di gantse

00:16:50.328 --> 00:16:52.383
mishpokhe velkhe ze'mir geven dort.

00:16:52.438 --> 00:16:54.383
un oykhet fardint a por

00:16:54.397 --> 00:16:57.958
LEI, un azoy hot men gelebt.

00:16:59.643 --> 00:17:09.369
un mayne shvester in Siget zenen zikh shoyn gevorn gresere meydlekh, hobn zey zikh baklert, vos haltn zey di mame mit di kinder

00:17:09.506 --> 00:17:13.260
azoy vayt dort fun dorf, in Rozavlye?

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:18.547
zey zeen do a shtikl voynung, nu, me zol araynkumen aher keyn Siget.

00:17:19.123 --> 00:17:24.068
azoy, in toyznt nayn hundert naynem un tsvontsik,

00:17:25.191 --> 00:17:28.630
hot men bashtetikt, mir kum'mir arayn keyn

00:17:28.767 --> 00:17:35.411
Siget. nu, deys tsien iz oykhet, vi azoy me zogt bay mentshn,

00:17:35.424 --> 00:17:39.452
me hot genumen a vogn, deys iz zibenem un draysik kilometer,

00:17:39.698 --> 00:17:41.767
hot men genumen a vogn,

00:17:41.794 --> 00:17:45.506
un der balebos hot geheysn oykhet Fishman,

00:17:45.671 --> 00:17:48.465
vi azoy hot er shoyn geheysn? Fayvish Fishman,

00:17:48.986 --> 00:17:54.945
un yener hot gehat aza, azoy hot es geheysn UNK, azoy hot men gerufn, aza langn vogn.

00:17:55.150 --> 00:17:58.821
un a dort hot men aropgeleygt di ale

00:17:58.821 --> 00:18:02.657
tshorbes, vi azoy me zogt, vos hobn zey gehat in shtub,

00:18:02.657 --> 00:18:05.068
un oyf der nakht

00:18:05.068 --> 00:18:08.068
hot men gerirt, vayl er,

00:18:08.068 --> 00:18:11.958
tsu fri hot gebroykht onpakn andere skhoyre,

00:18:11.958 --> 00:18:14.575
tsuriktsubrengen in dorf arayn.

00:18:14.575 --> 00:18:19.917
nu, ho'mir zikh, undz oyf dem vogn ale bazetst,

00:18:19.945 --> 00:18:23.232
un biz tsu fri iz men geforn, geforn,

00:18:23.246 --> 00:18:28.178
ikh gedenk azoy vi haynt, ikh bin ongekumen denstmol hob ikh derzen dos ershte mol in mayn lebn

00:18:28.178 --> 00:18:30.698
CHASHMAL, lemp,

00:18:30.745 --> 00:18:32.579
in velkhes yor iz dos geven?

00:18:30.767 --> 00:18:32.390
fun CHASHMAL.

00:18:32.397 --> 00:18:35.082
toyznt nayn hundert naynem un tsvontsik.

00:18:35.566 --> 00:18:37.835
toyznt nayn hundert naynem un tsvontsik.

00:18:36.828 --> 00:18:39.067
bist ge- alt geven tsen yor.

00:18:38.142 --> 00:18:39.787
tsen yor, yo.

00:18:39.821 --> 00:18:43.356
un ven ikh bin nokh geven azoy vi aroys fun der shtot,

00:18:43.438 --> 00:18:45.150
hob ikh gezen di

00:18:45.150 --> 00:18:48.780
groyse likhtikeyt, dos iz geven far mir aza

00:18:48.780 --> 00:18:50.150
a naye velt,

00:18:50.150 --> 00:18:52.287
mit dos ven, azoyns hob ikh nisht gezen,

00:18:52.315 --> 00:18:57.219
un ven ikh bin ongekumen shoyn in shtot, zenen zikh dey oysgeloshn, vayl se hot zikh shoyn gemakht tog.

00:18:57.219 --> 00:18:58.986
un ikh hob deys nisht shoyn akht genumen,

00:18:58.986 --> 00:19:01.383
un iz shoyn gevorn oys. nu.

00:19:01.890 --> 00:19:05.274
azoy ze'mir ongekumen, un dort hot undz gevart

00:19:05.315 --> 00:19:07.109
a shtub mit a kokh.

00:19:07.260 --> 00:19:10.178
azoy vi azoy me hot gekent,

00:19:10.178 --> 00:19:11.863
a shtub mit a kokh,

00:19:11.863 --> 00:19:15.342
vi azoy men zogt, in di shlangen gas, numere fuftsn,

00:19:15.534 --> 00:19:21.411
un in der shlangen gas hot haynt, hot zi a nomen, vayl in yener gas hot gevoynt

00:19:21.534 --> 00:19:22.972
Elye Vizl.

00:19:23.438 --> 00:19:25.534
er hot gevoynt in ek gas,

00:19:25.534 --> 00:19:29.698
un undz, nor er iz geven, ikh hob im denstmol nisht gekent, nisht fun dem iz di rede, nor

00:19:29.698 --> 00:19:32.164
yener gas, numere fuftsn.

00:19:32.164 --> 00:19:34.411
nu, dort ho'mir gevoynt

00:19:34.411 --> 00:19:35.671
di sh- meydlekh

00:19:35.671 --> 00:19:37.890
di shvester zenen gegangen arbetn,

00:19:37.986 --> 00:19:40.356
undz ho'mir dort gevoynt, un ikh

00:19:40.356 --> 00:19:41.602
gerekhnt tsu geyn

00:19:41.602 --> 00:19:43.602
oykhet in kheyder, vayter,

00:19:43.863 --> 00:19:45.712
nu. koydem,

00:19:45.753 --> 00:19:51.904
hobn mir gehat dort a bakantn, eynem Nokhem Feldman, vos der iz geven, er iz geven a balebos.

00:19:51.904 --> 00:19:55.493
er hot gehat, zayn vayb iz geven

00:19:55.493 --> 00:19:59.120
fun Rozavlye a shokhnte fun undz.

00:19:59.835 --> 00:20:06.178
un zey zenen geven raykher fun undz, nisht fun dem iz di rede, nor me hot undz gekent, iz yene hot undz oykh gekent.

00:20:06.187 --> 00:20:09.017
nu ze'mir ayngekumen, s'iz dokh nisht geven fun vos

00:20:09.167 --> 00:20:11.544
tsu lebn, nisht gehat vos tsu esn a shtikl broyt

00:20:11.727 --> 00:20:13.222
in shtub hot men gebroykht.

00:20:13.762 --> 00:20:17.321
nu, bin ikh gegangen tsu dem Nokhem Feldman, tsun ir az

00:20:17.378 --> 00:20:19.567
me zol zen epes arbet, zey hobn gehat a

00:20:19.616 --> 00:20:21.139
bir fabrik.

00:20:21.660 --> 00:20:24.978
nu, hot men mikh genumen, a tsen-yeredik yingl, hot men mikh genumen

00:20:24.997 --> 00:20:26.627
un gevashn flesher.

00:20:27.157 --> 00:20:32.442
dort hot men gevashn mit di hent, me hot gehat aza bershtele, aza randn bershtele hot men arayngeshtupt,

00:20:32.442 --> 00:20:33.937
un do hot men es azoy

00:20:33.995 --> 00:20:35.007
gedreyt,

00:20:35.104 --> 00:20:36.309
dort hob ikh

00:20:36.676 --> 00:20:38.633
gevashn a gantsn tog

00:20:39.424 --> 00:20:43.985
flesher, un ikh hob mikh bakumen a por LEI far dem.

00:20:45.220 --> 00:20:47.612
ven dort iz shoyn nisht geven azoy,

00:20:47.689 --> 00:20:49.810
iz geven eyner vos hot gemakht

00:20:50.138 --> 00:20:51.247
shtrikn.

00:20:51.488 --> 00:20:52.929
veyst vos heyst shtrikn?

00:20:52.757 --> 00:20:53.713
CHEVEL

00:20:53.668 --> 00:20:57.294
yo, azoy lange, grobe shtrikn, lang-, farshidene erley.

00:20:57.381 --> 00:21:01.605
nu, ahin bin ikh oykh gegangen arbetn, s'iz geven in a keler,

00:21:01.720 --> 00:21:04.382
in der, azoy hot es geheysn di SZINHAZ gas.

00:21:04.662 --> 00:21:09.165
nu, oykh dort gearbet un oykh dort fardint a por LEI.

00:21:09.522 --> 00:21:13.100
in der tsayt, bin ikh gegangen in kheyder vayter.

00:21:13.823 --> 00:21:15.386
kheyder dort iz geven,

00:21:15.598 --> 00:21:17.777
azoy gerufn, a talmed toyre.

00:21:17.912 --> 00:21:19.513
deys iz geven,

00:21:19.677 --> 00:21:21.905
dort hot men nisht gebroykht tsoln.

00:21:21.934 --> 00:21:24.885
vayl deys hot gehaltn di kehile,

00:21:25.290 --> 00:21:28.684
hot deys getsolt. nu, dort bin ikh gegangen,

00:21:28.858 --> 00:21:32.127
geven a gut, vi me zogt, a guter

00:21:32.166 --> 00:21:35.927
lerer, ikh zog nisht deys zogn andere,

00:21:36.756 --> 00:21:46.274
nu, un ven ikh bin shoyn greser gevorn, bin ikh shoyn aribergegangen in an ander kheyder, in a greser kheyder, vi me zogt, in a beser kheyder, Eyts Khaim, azoy hot es geheysn,

00:21:46.419 --> 00:21:48.300
deys iz geven in a shul,

00:21:48.483 --> 00:21:51.636
dort di rebe hot geheysn, mayn rebe, Dovid.

00:21:51.800 --> 00:21:55.870
er iz geven a ⟨borsher⟩, geven a guter rebe,

00:21:56.285 --> 00:21:58.599
un tsu fri

00:21:58.599 --> 00:22:04.665
fleg men alts geyn, arum zeks, ven s'iz nokh geven tunkl, zog mir, vinter, ober afile zumer, zeks,

00:22:04.733 --> 00:22:08.571
vayl zibn ze'mir shoyn geven in kheyder, dort hot men gelernt,

00:22:08.638 --> 00:22:14.598
un arum halb akht, zeyger akht, hot men gemakht a

00:22:15.360 --> 00:22:16.384
HAFSAKA.

00:22:15.813 --> 00:22:17.559
HAFSA- HAFSAKA,

00:22:17.578 --> 00:22:23.133
un m'iz arayngegangen davenen, vayl dort lebn undz iz takn geven di shul, UNK durkhgeyn a tir.

00:22:23.191 --> 00:22:25.901
un me hot dort gedavnt un

00:22:26.335 --> 00:22:29.016
me hot gegebn dort a KAFE,

00:22:29.131 --> 00:22:33.616
tsu trinken azoy umzist, far deye kinder, mit vos ven,

00:22:32.572 --> 00:22:33.427
gut.

00:22:33.956 --> 00:22:37.005
ikh ikh vil fr- fregn a epes.

00:22:37.584 --> 00:22:40.346
vos gedenkstu fun di yontoyvim

00:22:40.520 --> 00:22:41.547
in der heym?

00:22:41.547 --> 00:22:42.911
vi es iz geven?

00:22:42.295 --> 00:22:47.377
yo, zeyer gut ir hot mir geshtelt dey frage, vayl ikh hob aroysgelozt in Rozavlye,

00:22:48.149 --> 00:22:50.753
flegn mir alts geyn in shul.

00:22:50.753 --> 00:22:53.385
azoy gedenk ikh di shul azoy vi haynt,

00:22:53.781 --> 00:22:58.207
oyf rosheshone, oyf yomkiper, oyf peysekh,

00:22:58.207 --> 00:23:05.286
flegn aheymkumen di ale yinglekh velkhe zenen geven avekgeforn in der Rum- in di velt, vi azoy me zogt,

00:23:05.411 --> 00:23:09.577
fardinen gelt, velkhe zey hobn gearbet, vayl in Rozavlye iz nisht geven vu

00:23:09.577 --> 00:23:10.686
tsu arbetn.

00:23:10.792 --> 00:23:16.366
fun yeder mishpokhe zenen geven eyns, tsvey yinglekh, vifl yinglekh zenen geven azoy gevaksn,

00:23:16.366 --> 00:23:18.179
zenen zikh tsegangen in der velt.

00:23:18.324 --> 00:23:22.114
un deys iz geven, vi azoy me zogt, a gesheenish in in dorf,

00:23:22.182 --> 00:23:23.310
zenen ongekumen,

00:23:23.310 --> 00:23:26.328
der iz aheymgekumen, yener iz aheymgekumen,

00:23:26.348 --> 00:23:33.976
un in shul hot men di ale gezen, ikh, zog mir aza yingl vi ikh, hob gekukt oyf deye, oyf dey kumen, un zey geyt, un vos ven,

00:23:34.381 --> 00:23:40.042
un ahin iz gegangen mayn mame, hot, dort iz geven di vayberishe shuln, iz geven ekster,

00:23:40.129 --> 00:23:47.681
un dort hot men gedavnt, vi azoy me zogt, s'iz geven in sh- in in derfl iz geven tsvey shuln, nor ikh bin gegangen in der

00:23:47.737 --> 00:23:49.975
groyser shul, azoy hot zi geheysn.

00:23:50.023 --> 00:23:52.013
vayl zi iz geven noent tsu mir un

00:23:52.048 --> 00:23:56.581
mir hot shtendik gefeln, vi azoy me zogt, ikh hob ge- a khazn tsu hern,

00:23:56.581 --> 00:24:00.650
dort iz nisht geven direkt a khazn, nor der nign vi azoy me hot gedavnt.

00:24:00.824 --> 00:24:04.305
deys iz geven bayn undz, vi azoy me zogt, der vizhnitser

00:24:04.633 --> 00:24:08.597
nign vayl di khasidim, di fun undzer dorf

00:24:08.597 --> 00:24:10.989
zenen geven khasidim fun Vizhnits.

00:24:11.046 --> 00:24:16.003
azoy der gantser nign funem davenen, un funem lernen, iz geven azoy di

00:24:16.003 --> 00:24:18.048
bay Vizhnits.

00:24:20.131 --> 00:24:22.513
tsugevendt tsu der rosheshone,

00:24:22.542 --> 00:24:25.261
dos vel ikh keyn mol nisht fargesn a zakh,

00:24:25.830 --> 00:24:30.835
azoy vi ikh bin geven azoy a yingl, hot mikh eyner, a mentsh fun

00:24:30.835 --> 00:24:33.314
ahintsir fun undz, nisht vayt fun undz,

00:24:33.314 --> 00:24:36.834
gerufn ikh zol im geyn helfn khapn fish.

00:24:36.901 --> 00:24:38.666
oyf roshesho- oyf yontoyvim.

00:24:38.724 --> 00:24:42.148
vayl dort bayn undz iz geven a a taykh.

00:24:42.254 --> 00:24:45.214
a taykh vu s'iz gerunen a groys vaser.

00:24:45.214 --> 00:24:47.153
dort iz geven fish oykhet.

00:24:47.336 --> 00:24:50.673
un ikh bin gegangen mit im, geven a

00:24:50.673 --> 00:24:54.627
klener yingl, a kleyn yingl, nu ikh bin gegangen mit im, aroys funem dorf,

00:24:54.627 --> 00:24:58.561
un der hot dort arayngevorfn sam in vaser,

00:24:58.609 --> 00:25:01.049
un di fishn hot men nor gebroykht

00:25:01.223 --> 00:25:03.518
tsamkloybn, azoy vos ven.

00:25:03.518 --> 00:25:07.231
nu, vayl ikh hob im dort gehelf- geholfn, dos arbet,

00:25:07.231 --> 00:25:12.149
iz ze'mir aheymgekumen, zey hobn gehat geshokhtn a kelbl, tsu a ku, ikh veys vos ven,

00:25:12.149 --> 00:25:14.194
un me hot mir gegebn di leber.

00:25:14.493 --> 00:25:19.035
mit der leber bin ikh azoy aheymgegangen, mit a a a

00:25:19.180 --> 00:25:21.349
bletl untergehaltn,

00:25:21.378 --> 00:25:24.233
un azoy bin ikh gegangen oyf der gas biz aheym,

00:25:24.233 --> 00:25:27.435
ikh hob nisht gekukt tsi mikh zet men, tsi me zet nisht, mit vos ven,

00:25:27.435 --> 00:25:33.385
un mayn mame, s'iz geven a, me hot gekent makhn a gutn esn, mit dos ven,

00:25:33.385 --> 00:25:35.381
s'iz geven punkt far rosheshone.

00:25:36.577 --> 00:25:40.813
un rosheshone tsu fri, me gey'mir yeder avek in in

00:25:41.032 --> 00:25:42.787
shul arayn,

00:25:43.260 --> 00:25:48.098
un azoy arum nayn, tsen, ikh shpir mir vert shlekhts.

00:25:48.815 --> 00:25:51.380
ikh ver shlekht un shlekht,

00:25:51.959 --> 00:25:57.051
un ikh gey aroys, un tseleyg mikh,ahin far der shul iz geven aza

00:25:57.051 --> 00:26:01.139
shteyner vos mit vos me fleg alts farrikhtn dem shtroz.

00:26:01.226 --> 00:26:03.232
dort zenen geven tsamgeleygt di shteyner.

00:26:03.232 --> 00:26:05.228
un ikh tseleyg mikh oyf aza,

00:26:05.228 --> 00:26:06.607
dey shteyner,

00:26:06.714 --> 00:26:09.356
un ikh bin sh-, vi me zogt, shir

00:26:09.414 --> 00:26:11.343
fartik, vos ven.

00:26:11.719 --> 00:26:14.776
ikh hob fardorbn di mogn.

00:26:15.229 --> 00:26:19.164
un heybt on aroystsugebn, zolt mir antshuldik zayn,

00:26:19.164 --> 00:26:22.124
un me ruft mayn mame aroys fun der shul,

00:26:22.288 --> 00:26:24.034
un me firt mikh aheym,

00:26:24.545 --> 00:26:29.945
un mayn mame, vos ken zi tun? ikh hob oysgebrokhn. nokh mitog,

00:26:30.186 --> 00:26:33.166
dort in dorf iz geven a froy,

00:26:33.253 --> 00:26:38.856
zenen geven Shmul-Elye Shtern, deye zenen geven i frume, ober i raykhe oykh.

00:26:39.435 --> 00:26:44.450
dey froy, dey hot UNK a farshtendlekhe froy, dey hot men geheysn, vi azoy me zogt

00:26:44.479 --> 00:26:46.504
di hot aroysgeholfn

00:26:46.639 --> 00:26:49.108
iberol, oyf vos me hot gebroykht.

00:26:49.108 --> 00:26:52.994
hot men gebroykht zi zol dir gebn a shtikl broyt, hot zi gegebn a shtikl broyt.

00:26:52.994 --> 00:26:56.784
hostu gebroykht zolst ir gebn an eytse, hot zi dir gegebn an eytse.

00:26:56.986 --> 00:27:01.914
zogt mayn mame, zi geyt ariber. vi azoy, ikh gedenk shoyn nisht vi azoy zi hot geheysn.

00:27:01.914 --> 00:27:04.701
nu Shmul-Elye's vayb, Shmul-Elye Shtern's vayb.

00:27:04.769 --> 00:27:09.330
geyt ariber nokh ir, un zi kumt takn. undz ho'mir gevoynt, vi azoy me zogt, azoy

00:27:09.350 --> 00:27:11.221
oyf a bergl. nisht, nisht

00:27:11.221 --> 00:27:13.574
lebn hoypt shtroz. oyf a bergl.

00:27:13.988 --> 00:27:18.058
un zi kumt. un zi zet mikh, azoy.

00:27:19.071 --> 00:27:22.195
zogt zi, er hot zikh fardorbn di mogn, zogt zi.

00:27:22.243 --> 00:27:26.438
azoy vi azoy zi kukt mikh on. geheysn mir ne- vayzn di tsung, mit vos ven.

00:27:26.728 --> 00:27:31.743
ikh hob nisht gevust, koydem, az fun vos veyst zi az ikh hob fardorbn, vos ven?

00:27:32.360 --> 00:27:36.449
dertseylt zi far mayn mame, az zi hot mikh gezen nekhtn

00:27:36.545 --> 00:27:39.236
ven ikh bin gekumen mit der leber,

00:27:39.236 --> 00:27:42.264
hot zi mikh gezen funem fentster, fun ir,

00:27:42.264 --> 00:27:44.000
vi ikh bin durkhgegangen,

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:48.388
hot zi zikh shoyn forgeshtelt, az fun yener leber hob ikh mikh fardorbn

00:27:48.552 --> 00:27:49.545
di mogn.

00:27:50.152 --> 00:27:57.202
nu, azoy az, nu hot men mir gegebn, ikh gedenk shoyn vos ven, tsu trinken, vos ven ober...

00:27:58.350 --> 00:27:59.453
nor dem gekumen.

00:28:00.365 --> 00:28:05.689
nu, deys, deys iz geven, vi azoy me zogt fun di

00:28:05.689 --> 00:28:11.697
shuln, ober deys iz nisht geven eyn mol, ikh meyn, tsu geyn in shul, deys iz geven a shtendike, deys iz geven bay mir

00:28:11.697 --> 00:28:14.860
vi azoy me zogt, oykhet a nusekh azoy vi bay ale y-

00:28:14.860 --> 00:28:17.030
yidishe kinder,

00:28:17.030 --> 00:28:22.411
hobn gebroykht geyn, zenen gegangen in shul, afile me hot nisht gefregt, tsi nisht gefregt, di mame

00:28:22.411 --> 00:28:27.156
iz nisht a mol geven aza frage, tsi me geyt in shul, tsi me geyt nisht in shul, avade

00:28:27.233 --> 00:28:28.544
geyt men in shul.
